-- Toyota Recalls 599,029 Autos in Japan for Problems With Fuel Pumps, Brakes
-- B y   T a k u   K a t o
-- 2010-10-21T05:14:29Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-21/toyota-recalls-599-029-vehicles-in-japan-for-fuel-pumps-brakes.html
Toyota Motor Corp. recalled 599,029
vehicles in Japan, including Lexus models, because of problems
with the cars’ fuel pumps and brakes, according to a statement
today on the website of the nation’s transport ministry.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Taku Kato in Tokyo at 
